TEXT.S: = Tongan = Gaga mniq Nantowseyn Jnaysyang ka alang tongan. 278 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 952 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 88% niqan 841 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 12% niqan 111 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Seejiq/Seediq/Sediq71%, Tayal9%, Amis2%, Bunun3%, Paiwan1%, Truku1%, ni rahuq na o 1%.
